{"tid":33471,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"掛住過左身既親人可以點","createTime":"2016-12-10T20:06:48.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T01:05:26.000Z","uid":55410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ee7939d6817038cb93a67e9578e1d8994c335d13","tid":33471,"uid":55410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T20:06:48.000Z","msg":"本身全日都冇咩特別 三點幾都唔多訓得著 係頭先臨訓果一下突然諗起過左身既呀公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n起身喊一場先舒服曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似鬆左咁<br />\n但本身同呀公感情唔算深 佢走果陣都冇流過一滴眼淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n純粹抒發下 應該有至少三年冇喊過"},{"pid":"75625f021be080639c03951302249664964ce44c","tid":33471,"uid":4702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T20:09:45.000Z","msg":"未放低?"},{"pid":"f392dad38f1c504a949ffc31026b6b9d55c91428","tid":33471,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T20:10:40.000Z","msg":"走左幾耐<br />\n我嫲嫲走果陣成日都發夢見到佢死(唔同死法)<br />\n我覺得好困擾<br />\n不過過左排就冇野"},{"pid":"ce369e78f327812c087b911f408ee343f32397ab","tid":33471,"uid":55410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T20:12:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未放低?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一直以為冇咩感情架喎"},{"pid":"476fd485adc446b9513a583506ba0108ff8fe3f4","tid":33471,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T20:13:57.000Z","msg":"我呀婆都85，由細湊到我大<br />\n我都驚都佢走嗰陣我會好低落"},{"pid":"a5e68925e38f15085d6c67b4c39d73e6c31e3e8f","tid":33471,"uid":55410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T20:14:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>走左幾耐<br />\n我嫲嫲走果陣成日都發夢見到佢死(唔同死法)<br />\n我覺得好困擾<br />\n不過過左排就冇野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n走左差唔多一年啦 上年2月岩岩過完年就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我又冇發夢喎 係臨訓前突然閃過佢個樣 d眼淚就自己流<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07f6e4fbd87d4508279c4f382144f478c5f94c57","tid":33471,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T20:20:52.000Z","msg":"我都好掛住我阿公，佢今年年頭走左，<br />\n由細一齊住到大，感情好深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c02a1bc33e6281592d9180493c1a15adce1c3564","tid":33471,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T20:22:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>走左幾耐<br />\n我嫲嫲走果陣成日都發夢見到佢死(唔同死法)<br />\n我覺得好困擾<br />\n不過過左排就冇野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n走左差唔多一年啦 上年2月岩岩過完年就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我又冇發夢喎 係臨訓前突然閃過佢個樣 d眼淚就自己流<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗我斷斷續續發夢都有兩年<br />\n平時坐車經過佢生前住果度都會sad一sad<br />\n因為佢都走得好突然 臨走之前果晚成家上去探佢佢仲叫我地坐多陣先走<br />\n<br />\n我要好耐先放得低 點解果陣唔坐多陣先"},{"pid":"bbe18450fb40d2d9a5aec9395b18496ca66373fa","tid":33471,"uid":218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T20:22:56.000Z","msg":"係咪佢都掛住你<br />\n俾訊息你叫你拜吓佢"},{"pid":"cef88ab2218904afc0e91e0e563d3ffd602943c5","tid":33471,"uid":17213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T20:23:58.000Z","msg":"我就睇化左，遲早有日我都會去搵佢地，所以無太大感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07baec1d6ed5d1550a5a8faf7286791723994a66","tid":33471,"uid":47758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T20:25:55.000Z","msg":"有時喊下渲洩下都係好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b1c9669380d9c43464b70eedef11cc1818679a","tid":33471,"uid":52410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T20:26:16.000Z","msg":"你地咁掛住唔落去陪佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13fc2fc2381d3368c7158510a904c67c56c612a9","tid":33471,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T20:26:20.000Z","msg":"發夢"},{"pid":"26ab46ad39b0a3901afba9140d6bd623ae6901ac","tid":33471,"uid":39208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T20:34:35.000Z","msg":"十年前阿爺走無送佢最後一程 好後悔<br />\n<br />\n五年前阿嫲走我射波送佢<br />\n<br />\n諗番起又有少少sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6597b0441f7fc1ed8ddf3a16cde013b7475e44a","tid":33471,"uid":60361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T20:58:49.000Z","msg":"老豆cancer走左差唔多一年，由佢走嗰日開始到依家晚晚臨瞓之前都諗起佢，諗下以前同佢兩父子去釣下魚，睇下戲，行下街，有時會眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次唔覺意見到啲相，或者間唔中見到啲嘢都會無端端認起佢，個心好酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到呢一刻都覺得自己對佢唔住，佢住醫院嗰陣都唔識珍惜，掛住拍拖，去玩<br />\n佢吩咐幫佢買嘢食，download啲戲比佢喺醫院睇又冇幫佢做，到真係記得，幫佢整好曬埋，已經係佢身體最差嗰段日子，戲都睇唔切就走左<br />\n個腦成日諗起佢臨走前一晚，瞓醒斷左片嗰15分鐘連我都唔認得，真係好心酸<br />\n到呢一刻自己都原諒唔到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9baa2c6f29283fcc320a65c10c3e7355daaf415a","tid":33471,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T21:04:53.000Z","msg":"死先係回歸平靜"},{"pid":"f02adbca127d3d98cba727bafb466ef694ec5ae6","tid":33471,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T21:09:57.000Z","msg":"啊公走左幾年,有時都會掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢十幾個孫之中最錫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"029aaccedb2e9d4bcb2120fde92589ea9cf2c756","tid":33471,"uid":13330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T21:26:37.000Z","msg":"如果有方法見多一次<br />\n你又會想一直都見<br />\n珍惜時間啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce28e9bf7109835d573677565f4170c218053a51","tid":33471,"uid":61545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T01:05:26.000Z","msg":"當年老竇係我小學五年班個陣走咗<br />\n冇嘢嘅 時間耐咗去到考升中試就放低咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}